  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: f4de319ce92c2ba78b00a6d194d36091, type: 3}
  m_Name: TipTextGlobalConfig
  m_EditorClassIdentifier:
  <TipTextDatas>k__BackingField:
  - TipText: A stable network connection is recommended to ensure smooth gameplay and prevent data loss.
    ID: 566
  - TipText: Sign in to Game Center or Google Play Games to ensure your progress is always backed up securely.
    ID: 567
  - TipText: Did you know? Signing in to Game Center or Google Play Games lets you team up with others and join special events without any interruptions.
    ID: 568
  - TipText: Complete all of the shipper's orders to successfully pass the level.
    ID: 569
  - TipText: Support your team by donating up to 3 cards a day! It’s the fastest way to help everyone finish their card collections.
    ID: 570
  - TipText: Need a card? You can request one card from your team every day to help finish your collection quickly!
    ID: 571
  - TipText: Got a duplicate card? Don't worry! They turn into Star Points which you can use to get new card packs and complete your collection.
    ID: 572
  - TipText: Accidentally lost your progress? Use the Data Synchronization feature in Settings to recover your game data.
    ID: 573
  - TipText: Join the Foodie Sizzle Facebook group to get the latest updates, chat with fellow players, and share your achievements with the community!
    ID: 574
  - TipText: Keep your network stable to make sure your Hearts refill without interruption.
    ID: 575
  - TipText: Don't worry if you have to exit the game unexpectedly! Just ensure a stable connection, and you can pick up right where you left off.
    ID: 576
  - TipText: Ads not loading? Check your internet connection and restart the game to claim your rewards.
    ID: 577
  - TipText: When a shipper requests an order with chili, place the skewers on the red-hot grill to finish the order as quickly as possible!
    ID: 578
  - TipText: Enjoy Foodie Sizzle to the fullest! Buy the 'Remove Ads' pack in the Shop to disable interruptive ads.
    ID: 579
  - TipText: Don't forget to claim your Daily Reward! These extra Gold and Boosters will help you finish levels in no time.
    ID: 580
